1
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:38,192
I must be a terrible person, right?

2
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,280
You aren't terrible at all, Ran.

3
00:00:45,688 --> 00:00:47,690
You did the right thing,

4
00:00:50,680 --> 00:00:52,792
even if it’s painful.

5
00:00:55,910 --> 00:00:56,640
Yeah,

6
00:00:58,780 --> 00:01:00,440
it hurts a lot.

7
00:01:02,850 --> 00:01:05,128
It feels like no matter which way I turn, I’m always in the wrong.

8
00:01:12,170 --> 00:01:14,680
I believe in your decision.

9
00:01:20,940 --> 00:01:23,736
I think I’ll try talking to Mom first.

10
00:01:24,870 --> 00:01:29,448
If she agrees to back down quietly, I’ll leave it at that.

11
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:31,920
Ran

12
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:34,144
Yes?

13
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:39,488
If you can't handle it, want me to take care of it for you?

14
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:48,544
Mom and I have caused you enough trouble already.

15
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:53,744
Please let me handle this myself.

16
00:02:13,510 --> 00:02:14,200
Mom.

17
00:02:17,300 --> 00:02:18,648
Why are you back?

18
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:25,160
Do you even remember that I’m your mom?

19
00:02:27,752 --> 00:02:28,888
Mom, I..

20
00:02:28,928 --> 00:02:29,848
Get out!!

21
00:02:31,232 --> 00:02:33,230
After betraying me like this,

22
00:02:33,248 --> 00:02:34,952
why on earth would you come back, huh?!

23
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:38,592
Everything I did, I did for you.

24
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:41,392
You... You are just so stupid. Stupid,

25
00:02:41,432 --> 00:02:44,056
stupid, stupid! Truly stupid.

26
00:02:44,570 --> 00:02:45,848
But what you did was wrong.

27
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:47,192
You know that, right?

28
00:02:48,350 --> 00:02:50,776
I did everything for you!

29
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:03,328
It’s because I do understand you that

30
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,960
I’m here giving you a chance.

31
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:10,640
If you just agree to step down from the position gracefully,

32
00:03:11,350 --> 00:03:12,032
P’Chat and I..

33
00:03:12,056 --> 00:03:13,568
Why would I step down?!

34
00:03:13,608 --> 00:03:15,848
I have the appointment papers right here.

35
00:03:15,904 --> 00:03:17,144
Why would I ever step down?!

36
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:03,920
Ran.

37
00:04:05,610 --> 00:04:06,400
Yes?

38
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:11,192
How did things go with your mom?

39
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:15,720
I haven't had a chance to talk to her yet.

40
00:04:16,580 --> 00:04:19,032
Once she gets back,

41
00:04:19,670 --> 00:04:21,488
I’ll try speaking with her again.

42
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:24,544
If there’s any progress, I’ll let you know right away.

43
00:04:26,272 --> 00:04:27,040
Ranya...

44
00:04:30,060 --> 00:04:31,472
what happened to your face?

45
00:04:33,330 --> 00:04:34,712
It’s nothing.

46
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:35,872
Let me see.

47
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:43,008
Is your mom did?

48
00:04:47,010 --> 00:04:48,112
It’s fine, really.

49
00:04:48,690 --> 00:04:50,504
I’m sure she didn't mean to do it.

50
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:56,832
Just let me talk to her first,

51
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:01,384
okay?

52
00:05:08,660 --> 00:05:09,248
Fine.

53
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:22,800
I was a bit too hot-headed earlier today.

54
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:24,400
I’m sorry, dear.

55
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:30,184
Does it hurt much?

56
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,320
I’m so sorry.

57
00:05:34,460 --> 00:05:35,672
It’s okay.

58
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:39,088
It doesn't hurt that much anymore.

59
00:05:47,090 --> 00:05:49,160
Um... Mom?

60
00:05:50,180 --> 00:05:51,120
Yes, dear.

61
00:05:57,872 --> 00:05:59,560
Could you please resign?

62
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:05,224
I mean, everyone knows about your situation now.

63
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:08,992
I’m afraid they’re all going to look at you in a bad light.

64
00:06:12,150 --> 00:06:15,288
I don't care how anyone else looks at me.

65
00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:20,824
I just want you to be happy.

66
00:06:21,936 --> 00:06:24,840
Everything we stand to gain from this...

67
00:06:25,928 --> 00:06:27,930
it will belong to the two of us.

68
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,032
Mom...

69
00:06:31,530 --> 00:06:32,848
Mom, please, just stop.

70
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:40,024
I can forgive you for everything, you know.

71
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:45,424
We just need to forget all of this and start over.

72
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,512
As long as it’s the two of us,

73
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:55,064
there is no way Pimchat can steal what rightfully belongs to you.

74
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:58,976
But Mom, everything actually belongs to Pimchat.

75
00:07:00,690 --> 00:07:03,216
What is wrong with you?!

76
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:05,056
Always talking back to me.

77
00:07:05,740 --> 00:07:09,800
That company should belong to the two of us!

78
00:07:10,260 --> 00:07:11,040
Mom,

79
00:07:12,590 --> 00:07:14,104
listen to me.

80
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:18,280
If you just resign quietly,

81
00:07:19,410 --> 00:07:22,456
P’Chat said she won't take legal action against you.

82
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:26,448
Are you... Whose side are you on?

83
00:07:26,488 --> 00:07:27,552
Mine or hers?!

84
00:07:27,576 --> 00:07:29,296
Mom, please,

85
00:07:33,300 --> 00:07:34,752
come back and live with me.

86
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:42,096
Let’s just move out and live together, just the two of us.

87
00:07:44,336 --> 00:07:46,080
You don’t have to be afraid of anything,

88
00:07:47,230 --> 00:07:48,912
I’ll take care of you myself.

89
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:55,544
I already told you, I can’t back down now.

90
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:59,576
If I back down, I’m going to prison.

91
00:07:59,632 --> 00:08:01,024
Mom, Mom...

92
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,224
Mom, listen to me.

93
00:08:03,420 --> 00:08:06,520
P’Chat said that if you just come down willingly,

94
00:08:07,220 --> 00:08:10,200
she won’t call the police. Please, Mom.

95
00:08:14,730 --> 00:08:16,992
That’s only because she doesn’t know yet.

96
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:19,024
Know?

97
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:21,160
Know what?

98
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:30,904
Know that I was the one who killed her father...

99
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:33,672
all for the positions of both of us!

100
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:45,024
I can’t back down now, Ranya.

101
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:47,064
you have to pity me, dear.

102
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:50,808
If I back down, I’ll go to prison.

103
00:08:51,808 --> 00:08:54,064
You don’t want to see your mom in prison, do you?

104
00:08:54,470 --> 00:08:55,712
I'll be locked up.

105
00:08:55,744 --> 00:08:57,710
You wouldn't want that, would you, Ranya?

106
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,968
You are my daughter.

107
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:19,560
You are my child.

108
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:21,848
You are my daughter.

109
00:09:23,010 --> 00:09:24,448
I don’t want to go to prison!

110
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,104
Mom...

111
00:09:26,136 --> 00:09:27,784
You don't want me to go to prison, right?

112
00:09:27,832 --> 00:09:29,224
You have to help me. / Mom...

113
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:32,056
You have to help me. You must help your

114
00:09:32,290 --> 00:09:33,840
I don’t want to go to prison, please! / Mom...

115
00:09:34,780 --> 00:09:35,944
Mom... I need to go.
